    "analysis": "From the provided summary, all telemetry covers 2024-01-24T01:43:00 to 2024-01-24T02:07:00 UTC and there are many KPI types (cpu, mem, socket, diskio, workload, latency-50/90, error). The next step is to follow the preprocess rules: compute global thresholds (P95) per component-KPI using the full metric series (not filtered by incident window) but only for the candidate service-level components allowed by the task (ts-auth-service, ts-order-service, ts-route-service, ts-train-service, ts-travel-service). After thresholds are computed we should also know how many data points fall inside the incident window for each component-KPI to enable anomaly detection in the next step. No metrics filtering by incident window should occur before threshold calculation.",
